properties.Name: IncidentEventType
properties.Description:
A categorization of events that can occur in conjunction with an incident to create a 'history' of pre-defined events.

Ex:   
- Incident Reported
- Police Contacted
- Ambulance Contacted
- Repair Service Contacted
- Equipment Repaired
- Incident Location Secured
- Incident Reported to Authorities
- Incident Closed (Resolved)
- Incident Closed (Unresolved)

Columns.Name: IncidentEventTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Incident Event Type.

Columns.Name: IncidentEventTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of an Incident Event Type.

Columns.Name: IncidentEventTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of an Incident Event Type.
